HEADWORD: Cognovit
<hw>Cog*no"vit</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L., he has
acknowledged.]</ety> <fld>(Law)</fld> <def>An instrument in writing
whereby a defendant in an action acknowledges a plaintiff's demand to be
just.</def> <rj><au>Mozley & W.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

